Title: DMK cadres protest suspension of DMK MLAs from Assembly
Content: A group of Dravida Munnetra Kazhagam (DMK) cadres led by District secretary S. P. Diwakaran burnt the effigy of Assembly Speaker P. Dhanapal, protesting against the suspension of DMK MLAs in the State
Author: Special Correspondent
Description: A group of Dravida Munnetra Kazhagam (DMK) cadres led by District secretary S. P. Diwakaran burnt the effigy of Assembly Speaker P. Dhanapal, protesting against the suspension of DMK MLAs in the State
